  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的流程图，核心是从LMS门户开始，然后进入一个课堂服务的决策点。这个决策判断服务是否正常工作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以A是LMS门户，B是课堂服务的决策节点。这个决策的输出有两个分支：Yes和No，分别指向什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果服务正常（Yes），就进入成绩同步模块GradeSync，然后写入学生数据库StudentDB。如果服务异常（No），也要先到GradeSync，但这是一个修复流程，需要循环回B重新检测。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我梳理一下：Yes分支是B→C→E，C和E都是正常的GradeSync和StudentDB。No分支是B→D→B形成一个循环，D也是GradeSync但代表修复态。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，D和C其实是同一个GradeSync组件，但在流程里要区分正常路径和重试路径。循环直到服务检测通过，才走C那条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：A门户指向B决策点，B的Yes分支到C，C再到E学生库。No分支我先连到D。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "D回连到B的循环线我画好了。不过这里有个问题：D和C都是GradeSync，标签要不要区分？比如C叫\"正常同步\"，D叫\"修复后同步\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "暂时不用改标签，保持都叫GradeSync就行，通过路径上下文来区分。但帮我加一下无障碍说明，accTitle写\"Basic Flowchart Example\"，accDescr描述一下这个决策点和循环的逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加无障碍描述。accDescr我写成：A simple flowchart showing a decision point and loop until working, then shipping and celebrating. 这样覆盖了决策、循环直到正常工作、然后完成并庆祝的流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "accTitle",
        "accDescr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "\"shipping and celebrating\"有点俏皮，不过能体现流程完成的正向结果。最后确认一下循环逻辑：D必须回到B重新判断，不能绕过检测直接到E，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，D→B的连线已画好，没有D直接到E的捷径。整个结构是：A→B，B分Yes/No，Yes走C→E结束，No走D→B循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
